{"id":263143,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-中共十八大会议，成都上访维权者王荣文/","date":"2012-11-15T02:46:20Z","modified":"2012-11-15T02:46:20Z","title":"维权网 | 中共十八大会议，成都上访维权者王荣文“被旅游”49天（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员钟宏报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日早晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点半</span><span>，王蓉文被少城街办综治办主任李双全（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13981781567</span><span>）强行从厕所里面拖出后，与综治办王坚、段亚萍（女）一起送上一辆捷达车（车牌：川</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A.GLM72)</span><span>，从此踏上“被旅游”的旅程，直到十八大闭幕，王荣文才回到成都重获自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">   </span></div>\n<div><span>据王坚在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日晚上</span><span>在南充对王荣文说：“这次把你请出来旅游主要就是为了十八大维稳”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>据王荣文介绍：她先后“旅游”了南充、南部、阆中、雅安、天泉、名山、西昌、冕宁、盐源、攀枝花、再回到西昌，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>从西昌离开直到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日回到成都重获自由，历时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">49</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>王荣文说：旅游期间，吃：最贵的一餐大约耗费两百，便宜的时候四个人总共吃了三十多块钱。儿子在家中也无人照顾，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">49</span><span>天总共社区给儿子送了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>斤大米，五斤菜油。（注：王荣文儿子低保是被当局取消了的），</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日后，社区给她儿子一餐饭的餐劵，从周一到周五，每日只吃一餐，给了儿子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>元钱，用于周六和周日的饭钱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>王荣文吃腻了面条并要求回家，回宾馆后收拾行李打算回家，被三人拦下，并威胁说，这时你回去后，也会被关进农家乐，然后又软硬兼施，并答应给孩子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>元钱用于孩子的晚餐和周末的伙食。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>在旅游期间：他们住宾馆，最高的时候价格是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">400</span><span>多元一个标间，低的时候也是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>左右一个标间。捷达车一直载他们行使，行程</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span><span>多公里，加上油钱过路费至少应该花费了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>万元以上，如果再加上三个人的工资，那就更多了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>另外，王荣文被强制旅游回家后，发现孩子现在疑患自闭症。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OCG1fmYUUVw/UKRFb3ETMmI/AAAAAAAATg8/RnxdWFUGjyY/s1600/%E7%8E%8B%E8%8D%A3%E6%96%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E5%AF%B9%E9%95%9C%E8%87%AA%E6%8B%8D.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OCG1fmYUUVw/UKRFb3ETMmI/AAAAAAAATg8/RnxdWFUGjyY/s320/%E7%8E%8B%E8%8D%A3%E6%96%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E5%AF%B9%E9%95%9C%E8%87%AA%E6%8B%8D.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>王荣文被旅游</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-zWFZXqABHqA/UKRFdKRfhDI/AAAAAAAAThA/j93qTQ2IzsA/s1600/%E7%BB%BC%E6%B2%BB%E5%8A%9E%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%81%E7%8E%8B%E8%8D%A3%E6%96%87%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E4%BD%8D%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E5%9C%A8%E9%98%86%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-zWFZXqABHqA/UKRFdKRfhDI/AAAAAAAAThA/j93qTQ2IzsA/s320/%E7%BB%BC%E6%B2%BB%E5%8A%9E%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%81%E7%8E%8B%E8%8D%A3%E6%96%87%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E4%BD%8D%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E5%9C%A8%E9%98%86%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Yr2A-5BAn3g/UKRFej8PerI/AAAAAAAAThM/_0FILn_O8pQ/s1600/%E7%BB%BC%E6%B2%BB%E5%8A%9E%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%81%E7%8E%8B%E8%93%89%E6%96%87%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E4%BD%8D%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E5%9C%A8%E9%82%93%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%B3%E6%95%85%E5%B1%85%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"231\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Yr2A-5BAn3g/UKRFej8PerI/AAAAAAAAThM/_0FILn_O8pQ/s320/%E7%BB%BC%E6%B2%BB%E5%8A%9E%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%81%E7%8E%8B%E8%93%89%E6%96%87%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E4%BD%8D%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E5%9C%A8%E9%82%93%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%B3%E6%95%85%E5%B1%85%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>综治办押送王蓉文的三位领导在邓小平故居旅游</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2164184050119288698?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}